verbose_text: Furthermore, eosinophilic patients had significantly higher levels of FEV 1 and FVC than noneosinophilic patients (0.82 L (range : 0.63-1.04 L) versus 0.72 L (range : 0.56-0.97 L), P = 0.040; 1.52 L (range : 1.19-1.82 L) versus 1.30 L (range : 1.06-1.69 L), P = 0.011, respectively) (XREF_TABLE, XREF_FIG).
